{"tid":1360841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府網上電話簿　刪走大批警務人員聯絡資料","createTime":"2019-07-24T12:39:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T12:50:17.000Z","uid":114801,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"af1c1ce6b83d5fb24a9161ef1335be54ecc73b05","tid":1360841,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:39:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/政府網上電話簿-刪走大批警務人員聯絡資料/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E9%9B%BB%E8%A9%B1%E7%B0%BF-%E5%88%AA%E8%B5%B0%E5%A4%A7%E6%89%B9%E8%AD%A6%E5%8B%99%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E8%81%AF%E7%B5%A1%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%2F&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9VLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=f41d10a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E9%9B%BB%E8%A9%B1%E7%B0%BF-%E5%88%AA%E8%B5%B0%E5%A4%A7%E6%89%B9%E8%AD%A6%E5%8B%99%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E8%81%AF%E7%B5%A1%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%2F&h=4d1a5390\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/政府網上電話簿-刪走大批警務人員聯絡資料/</a><br />\n政府網上電話簿　刪走大批警務人員聯絡資料<br />\n<br />\n星期日白衫人在元朗追打市民，網上有片段顯示，八鄉分區指揮官李漢民曾和白衣人溝通，又和他們表示「心領」，之後李漢民在政府公開電話簿的聯絡資訊消失；《立場新聞》發現，除了李漢民外，元朗、八鄉、紅磡等多個分區，在分區指揮官以下，其他管理層的聯絡資訊大部份都消失。<br />\n<br />\n《立場》分別向政府新聞處和警察公共關係科查詢，刪除電話簿聯絡資料的原因，目前未有回覆。"},{"pid":"edbc9debe53d3094bf685c46426a1a2641cab19d","tid":1360841,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:41:12.000Z","msg":"之前係咪有巴打back up哂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e7b8bee0ba7cf1929de19d0278f1fbfaa07b81e","tid":1360841,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:43:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89886848e489bd88744fa8fa23951dabed2c5d3","tid":1360841,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c039cfe884feeb46d2ae7208fe84da7e626a68","tid":1360841,"uid":56729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:44:39.000Z","msg":"行得正企得正做乜怕本電話黃頁呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283718b4f4068c4402ce075bfeee2d0dcf43d959","tid":1360841,"uid":278391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:50:17.000Z","msg":"好簡單，對比番舊資料，刪除既全部係罪人"}]}